BE A PART OF THE GLOBAL LAUNCH OF THE URBAN BOUTIQUE VIB HOTEL IN THE DYNAMIC MIAMI ARTS & ENTERTAINMENT DISTRICT
USA Capital Management Inc, on behalf of Rebuild Miami – Edgewater, LLC, is offering to sell a minimum of $10 million and a maximum of $50 million in secured Notes to finance a portion of the development of a 245-room “Urban Boutique” hotel that will be affiliated with Best Western’s new VIB brand. Take advantage of this exciting opportunity benefiting from 8% interest bearing secured promissory notes collateralized by real estate assets.
The Notes are intended to be issued as an exempt Tier 2, Regulation A offering to both qualified accredited and non-accredited investors.The minimum individual Note purchase is $5,000.00 and each Note will be part of a series of Notes up to the maximum offering amount of $50 million. No funds will be accepted until a minimum of $10 million in Notes has been escrowed.Rebuild Miami – Edgewater, LLC is investing $20.9 million in equity.The hotel will be located on a ±1.2-acre site at the intersection of NE 2nd Avenue and NE 17th Street in the rapidly developing Arts & Entertainment District on the north side of the City of Miami’s Central Business District.



 
 

 
 
 
 

























