 CitiBusiness® Lockbox 
 Improve cash flow with ease and efficiency. 
 Hide product features Show product features


With CitiBusiness Lockbox, you can turn paper checks into available funds faster by allowing Citibank to receive them on your behalf at a designated P.O. Box. With CitiBusiness Lockbox you can:

Process and deposit your checks according to your detailed instructions
Collect mailed checks and credit card payments in one central location
Deposit checks into one or multiple accounts 
Access deposit and document images with CitiBusiness Online



