 Positive Pay/Match Pay 
 Add an extra layer of protection with this check fraud prevention feature that automatically compares details of checks written on your Citibank Checking account and compares them to the issue file you upload. 
 Hide product features Show product features


 You can approve or return any checks that do not match those in the issuance file. You'll get: 

A listing of checks that do not match your issuance file (exceptions) each day and the ability to Pay or Return them with a single click
Several options to meet the specific needs of different size businesses, including Positive Pay, Payee Positive Pay and Reverse Positive Pay
Ability to obtain software to assist in creating properly formatted issuance files



