 Citibank Zero-Balance Account 
 Seize greater control of your payments and collections with a Citibank Zero-Balance Account. 
 Hide product features Show product features


 Seize greater control of your payments and collections with a Citibank Zero-Balance Account. It lets you automatically transfer available funds to and from a general operating account at the end of each business day—allowing you to maximize the use of your funds. 


1-877-462-2484

