 Investment Sweeps 
 An Investment Sweep puts excess cash to work overnight, so you'll sleep... but your money won't. 
 Hide product features Show product features


 You select a target balance (can be $0) for your CitiBusiness Checking account and each day, funds above your target balanceFootnote 2 will be automatically transferred to a time-deposit investment where they can earn interest.  The balance will then be transferred back into your main operating account each morning. 


1-877-462-2484

